data.description: Welcome home to this renovated 3 bedroom, 2-bathroom home located near the CF College. The home features 1,649 SQFT of living space. As you come through the front door you will walk into the spacious living room with laminate flooring throughout.  Newer roof and HVAC system. Property is fully fenced, plenty of cabinet space in the kitchen, granite counter tops, an added pantry cabinet with bar top and a unique pass-through to the spacious family room. Call for an appointment today, this opportunity won't last!
